public static class TeamleDatabase.Converters extends Object
Defines converters for otherwise unsupported types (initially, just Instant) to one of those supported by Room/SQLite.

      @Nullable public static Long toLong(@Nullable Instant value)
      Returns the specified Instant value as a Long, corresponding to the number of milliseconds elapsed since 1970-01-01 00:00:00+00:00 encapsulated within value. When value is null, this method returns null as well.
      Parameters:
      value - Input Instant
      Returns:
      Epoch milliseconds encapsulated in value.

    • toInstant

      @Nullable public static Instant toInstant(@Nullable Long value)
      Returns an Instant instance containing the specified Long value epoch milliseconds. That is, value is interpreted as a number of milliseconds elapsed since 1970-01-01 00:00:00+00:00, and the corresponding Instant is returned. When value is null, this method returns null as well.
      Parameters:
      value - Epoch milliseconds.
      Returns:
      Instant corresponding to value.
